DIETARY NEEDS • RELIGIOUS PREFERENCES
Special meals can be provided for passengers who require them for
dietary needs or religious preferences, if advised in advance.
For Roman Catholic passengers on
Pan American. a special dispensation has been granted
by the Sacred Congregation of the Council whereby they
are not obligated to abstain from meat on Friday and other days of abstinence.
Our Kosher meals are prepared and packed under strict Orthodox
supervision in accordance with Jewish dietary law.
